{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"So it was about four years ago, five years ago,"},{"time":3000,"text":"I was sitting on a stage in Philadelphia, I think it was,"},{"time":5000,"text":"with a bag similar to this."},{"time":8000,"text":"And I was pulling a molecule out of this bag."},{"time":11000,"text":"And I was saying, you don't know this molecule really well,"},{"time":14000,"text":"but your body knows it extremely well."},{"time":17000,"text":"And I was thinking that your body hated it, at the time,"},{"time":21000,"text":"because we are very immune to this. This is called alpha-gal epitope."},{"time":24000,"text":"And the fact that pig heart valves have lots of these on them"},{"time":28000,"text":"is the reason that you can't transplant a pig heart valve into a person easily."}]},{"cues":[{"time":32000,"text":"Actually our body doesn't hate these."},{"time":34000,"text":"Our body loves these. It eats them."},{"time":37000,"text":"I mean, the cells in our immune system are always hungry."},{"time":40000,"text":"And if an antibody is stuck to one of these things"},{"time":44000,"text":"on the cell, it means \"that's food.\""},{"time":47000,"text":"Now, I was thinking about that and I said, you know, we've got this"},{"time":49000,"text":"immune response to this ridiculous molecule"},{"time":52000,"text":"that we don't make, and we see it a lot in other animals and stuff."},{"time":56000,"text":"But I said we can't get rid of it,"},{"time":59000,"text":"because all the people who tried to transplant heart valves"},{"time":61000,"text":"found out you can't get rid of that immunity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":63000,"text":"And I said, why don't you use that?"},{"time":65000,"text":"What if I could stick this molecule,"},{"time":68000,"text":"slap it onto a bacteria"},{"time":70000,"text":"that was pathogenic to me, that had just invaded my lungs?"},{"time":74000,"text":"I mean I could immediately tap into"},{"time":76000,"text":"an immune response that was already there,"},{"time":78000,"text":"where it was not going to take five or six days to develop it --"},{"time":81000,"text":"it was going to immediately attack whatever this thing was on."},{"time":84000,"text":"It was kind of like the same thing that happens when you,"},{"time":86000,"text":"like when you're getting stopped for a traffic ticket in L.A.,"},{"time":90000,"text":"and the cop drops a bag of marijuana in the back of your car,"},{"time":93000,"text":"and then charges you for possession of marijuana."},{"time":96000,"text":"It's like this very fast, very efficient way to get people off the street."}]},{"cues":[{"time":100000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":102000,"text":"So you can take a bacteria"},{"time":104000,"text":"that really doesn't make these things at all,"},{"time":106000,"text":"and if you could clamp these on it really well"},{"time":108000,"text":"you have it taken off the street."},{"time":110000,"text":"And for certain bacteria"},{"time":112000,"text":"we don't have really efficient ways to do that anymore."},{"time":114000,"text":"Our antibiotics are running out."},{"time":116000,"text":"And, I mean, the world apparently is running out too."},{"time":119000,"text":"So probably it doesn't matter 50 years from now --"},{"time":122000,"text":"streptococcus and stuff like that will be rampant --"},{"time":125000,"text":"because we won't be here. But if we are --"},{"time":127000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":129000,"text":"we're going to need something to do with the bacteria."}]},{"cues":[{"time":131000,"text":"So I started working with this thing,"},{"time":135000,"text":"with a bunch of collaborators."},{"time":137000,"text":"And trying to attach this to things that were"},{"time":140000,"text":"themselves attached to certain specific target zones,"},{"time":144000,"text":"bacteria that we don't like."},{"time":146000,"text":"And I feel now like George Bush."},{"time":150000,"text":"It's like \"mission accomplished.\""},{"time":152000,"text":"So I might be doing something dumb, just like he was doing at the time."},{"time":155000,"text":"But basically what I was talking about there we've now gotten to work."},{"time":159000,"text":"And it's killing bacteria. It's eating them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":163000,"text":"This thing can be stuck, like that little green triangle up there,"},{"time":167000,"text":"sort of symbolizing this right now."},{"time":170000,"text":"You can stick this to something called a DNA aptamer."},{"time":173000,"text":"And that DNA aptamer will attach specifically"},{"time":175000,"text":"to a target that you have selected for it."},{"time":177000,"text":"So you can find a little feature on a bacterium that you don't like,"},{"time":181000,"text":"like Staphylococcus -- I don't like it in particular,"},{"time":184000,"text":"because it killed a professor friend of mine last year."},{"time":187000,"text":"It doesn't respond to antibiotics. So I don't like it."},{"time":190000,"text":"And I'm making an aptamer that will have this attached to it."},{"time":193000,"text":"That will know how to find Staph when it's in your body,"},{"time":196000,"text":"and will alert your immune system to go after it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":199000,"text":"Here's what happened. See that line on the very top"},{"time":202000,"text":"with the little dots?"},{"time":204000,"text":"That's a bunch of mice that had been poisoned"},{"time":207000,"text":"by our scientist friends down in Texas,"},{"time":209000,"text":"at Brooks Air Base, with anthrax."},{"time":212000,"text":"And they had also been treated with a drug that we made"},{"time":215000,"text":"that would attack anthrax in particular,"},{"time":218000,"text":"and direct your immune system to it."},{"time":220000,"text":"You'll notice they all lived, the ones on the top line --"},{"time":222000,"text":"that's a 100 percent survival rate."},{"time":224000,"text":"And they actually lived another 14 days,"},{"time":227000,"text":"or 28 when we finally killed them,"},{"time":229000,"text":"and took them apart and figured out what went wrong."},{"time":232000,"text":"Why did they not die?"},{"time":234000,"text":"And they didn't die because they didn't have anthrax anymore."},{"time":237000,"text":"So we did it. Okay?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":239000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":241000,"text":"Mission accomplished!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":243000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}